description: A pleasant hike by the Larch Valley. Then the rise to the Sentinal Pass. From there a good view of the surrounding mountains. The descent to the Paradise Valley is very much strenuous and rough. It is badly marked. The way by the Paradise Valley is very nice again.
directions: Access Point: Moraine Lake Parking LotBack to the car by hitchhiking.
title: Larch Valley-Sentinal Pass- Paradise Valley
